  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "New 'Fireball' Raises",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "An Old Question: Do",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Flying Saucers Exist?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Californian, Who 'Talks' to Men",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "From the Stars, Says 'Yes';",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Scientists Assail Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "By ELLIOT CARLSON",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Staff Reporter of THE WALL STREET JOURNAL",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "They're back. The latest was sighted a few",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "nights ago by residents and pilots in the north-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "ern tier of states and Canada. They described",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "it as an orange fireball. The Air Force at first",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "called it an unidentified flying object, but now",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "says it was a meteor. Some other people",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "called it a flying saucer.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Several people say they saw the fireball last",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Tuesday night. An 11-year-old boy in Laramie,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Wyo., says he watched it drop into the woods",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "near his home. A woman in Elyria, Ohio,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "says she saw it plunge into a lake Michi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "gan. Scientists and police combed a 70-acre",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "area near Pittsburgh after a woman there saw",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "an object crash to earth \"smoldering.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Despite these witnesses and search efforts,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "however, the thing has yet to be found. In this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "regard, it is like all other unidentified flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "objects, or UFOs, which are mysterious be-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "cause they are seen but never found.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "Whatever it turns out to be-meteor, mirage,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "part, hoax, weather oddity or miss from",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Mars-it appeared in a banner year for such",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "objects. Unidentified objects disappeared from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "public consciousness following a rash of reports",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "of saucers in the mid-1950s. \"We've had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "more reports this year than in any year since",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "1957, when we had more than a thousand,\" says",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "a spokesman for Project Blue Book, the Air",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "Force program set up in 1948 to evaluate re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "ports of the phenomena.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "Men From Outer Space",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "Nobody knows what the objects are or where",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "they come from, but there is no lack of theories",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "of controversy. The Amalgamated Flying",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "Saucer Clubs of America, Inc., is sure the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "\"men\" come from outer space. How do",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "they know? The \"space people\" have told",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "It was only that, says Gabriel Green, who",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "runs the California group. \"Space people have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "given us information about life on other",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "stars and solutions to insurmountable prob-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "lems on our planet.\" One suggestion allegedly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "made to Mr. Green in 1960 by a visit from Al-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "bert, a Centaurian, a nearby star: Run for Pres-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "ident as a write-in candidate. (He campaigned",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "by, then decided not to run.)",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "The National Investigations Committee on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "Aerial Phenomena (NICAP), a private re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "search organization in Washington, doesn't",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "agree with that theory. \"We reject reports of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "beings landing on earth to solve all our",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "problems,\" says a spokesman. No men from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "Mars. \"We've got a lot of bunk.\" Not necessarily, says",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "the committee. It believes a Congressional in-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "vestigation would prove that UFOs \"are real",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "aerial objects...under the control of living",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "beings.\" As an afterthought, the spokesman",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "adds: \"There are a tremendous number of peo-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "ple who have been able to pinpoint them-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "selves as experts in this field because it's so con-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "troversial.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "One man who's not confused at all is Charles",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "A. Maney, professor emeritus of physics and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "mathematics at Defiance College in Ohio. Says",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "Maney: \"These objects are unquestion-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "ably from outer space.\" He bases his reason-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "ing on the fact that the objects often interfere",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "with electrical circuits, indicating to him",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "\"some means of propulsion associated with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "magnetic fields.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "\"There's Nothing To It\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "Such notions are scoffed at by astronomers,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "however. \"All this is imagination outside the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "realm of science,\" says Donald H. Menzel, di-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "rector of the observatory at Harvard. \"I have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "studied more than 1,000 Air Force cases and discovered that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "all have simple explanations in terms of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "known natural phenomena. There's not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "one, not hundreds. Some are quite spec-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "tacular, such as reflections from ice crystals or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "stars, searchlights on clouds or high-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "altitude spider webs. But to some people the idea",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "of flying saucers is a matter of religious",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "conviction,\" he says.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "Mr. Menzel reads more into the Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "text": "data than does the Air Force itself. Of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "text": "the 700 UFO reports made to the Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "text": "in 1964, 675 remain classified as \"unidenti-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "text": "fied.\" He defines this cate-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "text": "gory as containing sightings whose pertinent",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "text": "data can't be correlated with any known object",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "text": "or phenomenon.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "text": "\"The Air Force's approach disturbs some",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "text": "people, however. \"The Air Force should admit",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "text": "there are natural phenomena taking place un-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 106,
      "text": "der our noses of which we know nothing,\" says",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "text": "I. M. Levitt, director of Fels Planetarium at the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "text": "Franklin Institute in Philadelphia. He adds:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "text": "\"The Air Force is trying to explain something",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "text": "that isn't susceptible to explanation.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "text": "Robert Fleser, director of the Oklahoma Sci-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 112,
      "text": "ence and Art Foundation planetarium at Okla-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 113,
      "text": "homa City, believes \"the Air Force must have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 114,
      "text": "had its star-finder upside down during Aug-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 115,
      "text": "ust.\" When several reports of flying saucers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 116,
      "text": "were ascribed by the Air Force to sightings of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 117,
      "text": "stars. \"The constellations of Taurus and Orion",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 118,
      "text": "weren't visible at the time the Air Force said",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 119,
      "text": "the sightings were made. I think they made an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 120,
      "text": "error.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 121,
      "text": "The whole problem, says J. Allen Hynek,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 122,
      "text": "chairman of the department of astronomy at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123,
      "text": "Northwestern University and a consultant to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124,
      "text": "the Air Force, is that the matter should be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 125,
      "text": "studied more thoroughly.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 126,
      "text": "\"Pressure to conformity in academic cir-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 127,
      "text": "cles and fear of ridicule have slowed the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128,
      "text": "study,\" according to Robert Hall, a sociology",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129,
      "text": "professor at the University of Illinois in Chi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 130,
      "text": "cago.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 131,
      "text": "\"The possibility of life on Mars is an un-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 132,
      "text": "popular thing to consider three days,\" says",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 133,
      "text": "Frank B. Salisbury, a professor of plant phy-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 134,
      "text": "siology at Colorado State University. At the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 135,
      "text": "risk of being unpopular, Mr. Salisbury told the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 136,
      "text": "fifth annual Space Conference this year that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 137,
      "text": "\"there may be some natural explanation of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 138,
      "text": "these things, but a tentative possibility to be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 139,
      "text": "considered is that UFOs are spaceships from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 140,
      "text": "Mars.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141,
      "text": "Fueling the flying-saucer controversy has",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 142,
      "text": "been the large number of reports from what",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 143,
      "text": "many people consider reliable witnesses-pilots",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 144,
      "text": "with technical backgrounds. Since 1947, more",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 145,
      "text": "than 100 private, military and commercial pilots",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 146,
      "text": "have reported spotting strange objects in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 147,
      "text": "sky, according to one study.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 148,
      "text": "Pinning down such reports is difficult, how-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 149,
      "text": "ever. \"Some of the boys did report things they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 150,
      "text": "couldn't identify a few years ago,\" says a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 151,
      "text": "spokesman for American Airlines. \"But our",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 152,
      "text": "pilots haven't made a report for years.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 153,
      "text": "Nevertheless, \"we have on file a great num-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 154,
      "text": "ber of reports from pilots who want their",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155,
      "text": "names used but still want to tell somebody",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 156,
      "text": "what they've seen, claims J. B. Hartranft, Jr.,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 157,
      "text": "president of the Aircraft Owners and Pilots As-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 158,
      "text": "sociation. And he says: \"I haven't drawn any",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 159,
      "text": "conclusions myself, but I think we're certainly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 160,
      "text": "got a good mystery on our hands.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 161,
      "text": "4-18-66",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 162,
      "text": "\"Report Them...Forget It-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 163,
      "text": "I Have Enough Credibility Problems As It Is.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 164,
      "text": "Longon, Ontario Free Press 3-26-66",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 165,
      "text": "100 Wa`ch UFO",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
